# Test Yonko API Key Authentication
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7216
@remoteUrl = https://api.lifepadi.com

### Test 1: Valid API Key
GET {{remoteUrl}}/api/yonko/delivery-fee?Origin=Victoria Island&Destination=Ikeja
X-API-Key: dev-yonko-key-2025-external-access

### Test 2: Invalid API Key
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/yonko/delivery-fee?Origin=Victoria Island&Destination=Ikeja
X-API-Key: invalid-key

### Test 3: Missing API Key
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/yonko/delivery-fee?Origin=Victoria Island&Destination=Ikeja

### Test 4: Create with Valid API Key
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/yonko
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: dev-yonko-key-2025-external-access

{
  "pickUpAddress": "24 Ajao Rd, Lagos",
  "deliveryAddress": "7 Marina Rd, Lagos",
  "pickupType": "Normal",
  "deliveryFee": 1500,
  "customerFirstName": "John",
  "customerLastName": "Doe",
  "customerEmail": "john.doe@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "09123456789"
}

### Test 5: List with Valid API Key
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/yonko?pageNumber=1&pageSize=5
X-API-Key: dev-yonko-key-2025-external-access